      <title>法官阻止特朗普战时力量计划加快驱逐出境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/trump-invokes-wartime-powers-to-accelerate-deportations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官封锁了唐纳德·特朗普总统的计划，计划在数百年历史的移民法下加强对无证移民的驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/trump-invokes-wartime-powers-to-accelerate-deportations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 21:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Macron的批准率在IPSOS民意调查中跃升了5分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/macron-s-approval-rating-jumps-5-points-in-ipsos-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据Ipsos-Cesi Cessi Cessi工程学院的民意调查，总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）的批准率跃升了5分，因为法国公民对国际危机的担忧飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/macron-s-approval-rating-jumps-5-points-in-ipsos-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NHS英格兰报废后，更多的Quangos可能会在射击线上 - 街头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-15/more-quangos-could-be-in-firing-line-after-nhs-england-scrapped-streeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卫生部长说，报废NHS英格兰是“开始的，而不是目的”，誓言继续“削减肿的官僚机构”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-15/more-quangos-could-be-in-firing-line-after-nhs-england-scrapped-streeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 21:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在俄罗斯拒绝后缩小了特使到乌克兰战争的角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/trump-narrows-role-of-envoy-to-ukraine-war-after-russian-rebuff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周六表示，他正在将基思·凯洛格（Keith Kellogg）命名为他的乌克兰特别使节，在报道说，他在克里姆林宫（Kremlin）的要求中近期在美国 - 俄罗斯的谈判中被淘汰后，退休的将军的投资组合缩小了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/trump-narrows-role-of-envoy-to-ukraine-war-after-russian-rebuff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 20:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对也门的胡希战士发动军事罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/trump-orders-military-action-against-houthi-fighters-in-yemen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他下令对也门的遗址进行军事袭击，该地点被伊朗支持的霍蒂民兵所控制，几个月后损害了红海的运输车道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/trump-orders-military-action-against-houthi-fighters-in-yemen</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 19:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞族人在几十年来最大的抗议活动中反对Vucic统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/serbs-rally-against-vucic-regime-in-biggest-protest-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，成千上万的人在贝尔格莱德市中心大放异彩，以抗议由总统亚历山大·沃西奇（Aleksandar Vucic）领导的政府，这是塞尔维亚最近历史上最大的集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/serbs-rally-against-vucic-regime-in-biggest-protest-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 16:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默（Schumer）在关闭后撤退后领导聚会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/schumer-leads-party-at-odds-with-itself-after-shutdown-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）的呼吁避免了破坏性的政府关闭，这使唐纳德·特朗普总统的政策疏远了政治基础，并对党长老的谨慎回应感到沮丧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/schumer-leads-party-at-odds-with-itself-after-shutdown-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚极右翼领导人西蒙（Simion）为担任总统竞选而清理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/romanian-far-right-leader-simion-cleared-to-run-for-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚最大的极右翼政党的领导人将被允许参加五月的总统大选，此前他支持的前锋被禁止参加比赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/romanian-far-right-leader-simion-cleared-to-run-for-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 09:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Carney在与我们的裂谷中评论加拿大的F-35喷气式飞机的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/carney-reviews-canada-s-order-of-f-35-jets-amid-rift-with-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大新任总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）下令对该国与美国洛克希德·马丁公司（Lockheed Martin Corp）的合同进行F-35战斗机的合同，这是双方对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税和扩张主义言论的纠纷的新阵线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/carney-reviews-canada-s-order-of-f-35-jets-amid-rift-with-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 04:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Doge工作人员违反了国库规则传输个人数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/doge-staffer-broke-treasury-rules-in-transmitting-personal-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位联邦官员在周五的一份法庭文件中透露，政府效率部的一名工作人员在向特朗普政府中的其他两个人发送了包含个人信息的电子表格时违反了财政部的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/doge-staffer-broke-treasury-rules-in-transmitting-personal-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 20:07:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
